snippet.title: Boomerang Jack - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2010010/Boomerang_Jack/
Wishlist on Steam if interested in the game. It's the #1 thing that helps us out!

Boomerang Jack is a fast-paced character action game in a fantasy pirate world. Master the stylish hack-and-slash combat to wreak havoc on foes. Parkour across mysterious lands and battle all manner of creatures to uncover a dark, impending reality.

Follow us on twitter: https://twitter.com/boomjackgame
